  "instructions": [
    "Heat 1 tsp of sesame oil in a large pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 3-4 minutes.",
    "Add the pork cubes and cook until browned, about 5-6 minutes.",
    "Add the curry powder and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the curry sauce, soy sauce, sugar, and rice vinegar. Stir to combine.",
    "Bring the mixture to a simmer and cook for 10-15 minutes, or until the pork is tender.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve hot over steamed rice."
